des: AWS Skill enables customers to access curated executive content, leadership insights, practical use case and many more. Created to support business and IT executives in their role as a technology leader, it includes videos on how we Innovate at Amazon, Customer Success Stories, Executive Insights, and other thought provoking content on the changing role of technology in society today. The skill also lets you connect with key AWS leaders for a private 1:1 conversation on topics like Influencing Leadership, Innovate like Amazon, Security, Data Strategy, or any other business discussion.
